  "title": "BackShip - Delivery to a Collection Point",
  "urlName": "How-to-deliver-packages-to-BackShip-collection-points-in-France",
  "url": "https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/How-to-deliver-packages-to-BackShip-collection-points-in-France",
  "language": "en_GB",
  "lastPublishedDate": "2026-03-02T13:26:47.000Z",
  "topics": [],
  "bodyHtml": "<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Overview</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Back Market gives you the opportunity to have your parcels delivered to a Chronopost Collection Point, in addition to home delivery. This option is available exclusively through the BackShip service.</span></p>\n<h2><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Before activating this option, make sure you meet the following conditions:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You are subscribed to the BackShip service</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Your orders are local orders (no cross-border shipping)</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">France: available now via Chronopost</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">United Kingdom: available from April 2025 for UK sellers</span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Why activate Collection point delivery?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Collection Point delivery offers concrete benefits for both you and your customers:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 224px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 605px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Benefit</strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Detail</strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#128176; Lower cost</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Up to 55% cheaper than home delivery (e.g. smartphones) → better margin for you</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#128230; Fewer failed deliveries</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">50% fewer failed deliveries compared to home delivery</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#128274; Lower loss rate</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Loss/non-receipt rate of 0.54% vs 0.93% for home delivery</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#128722; Better conversion rate</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Customers appreciate this option and convert more</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How to activate Collection Point delivery?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Setup works exactly like any other BackShip delivery method - no additional configuration is required.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Follow this guide to add Collection Point as a delivery method: <span style=\"color: #3498db;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/Set-up-my-shipping-methods\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;\">Set up BackShip delivery methods</a>.</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer experience</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Once activated, Collection Point delivery appears as a delivery option on the Back Market website at checkout.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>The customer:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Selects the &quot;Collection Point&quot; option</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Chooses the nearest collection point to their registered address</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Completes their order as usual</span></li></ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">When the parcel arrives at the collection point, the customer receives email and SMS notifications.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Size limitations</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Not all parcels can be delivered to a collection point. Make sure your parcel meets the following requirements:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 565px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 264px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Criteria</strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Limit</strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Maximum weight</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">≤ 20 kg</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sum of all sides (2H + 2W)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">≤ 250 cm</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Maximum length</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">≤ 100 cm</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>⚠️ If these conditions are not met, the parcel will be refused by the collection point and will not be delivered.</em></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">What happens if the customer doesn&#39;t pick up their parcel?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer receives regular reminders to collect their parcel. Once the deadline below has passed, the parcel is returned to the sender (you):</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 358px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 252px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Collection Point type</strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Storage period</strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Chronopost or La Poste agency</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">14 days</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 43pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Chronopost partner collection point</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">8 days</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Consequences for the seller:</span></h2>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If a customer service request was opened within the deadline, the order is refunded to the customer</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The customer will need to place a new order if they still want the product</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">For any questions about your specific situation, open a ticket via the <span style=\"color: #3498db;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/submit-new-request\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;\">SSC</a></span></span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How does insurance work?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Insurance works the same way as for any BackShip shipment:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">It is optional</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">All parcels are covered by &quot;Ad valorem&quot; insurance (up to the declared value of the product)</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To find out more: <span style=\"color: #3498db;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/How-can-I-get-reimbursed-for-a-damaged-package-with-BackShip\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;\">How can I get reimbursed for a damaged package with BackShip?</a></span></span></p>\n<h2><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Returns &amp; billing</span></h2>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Returns: The standard process applies. The customer opens a customer service request within the required timeframe.</span>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To find out more: <span style=\"color: #3498db;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/Return-process\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;\">Returns processing</a></span></span></li></ul>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Billing: Identical to other BackShip delivery methods. </span>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To find out more: <span style=\"color: #3498db;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/How-to-understand-your-BackShip-invoices\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;\">Understanding your BackShip invoices</a></span></span></li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Need help?</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The BackShip team is available to assist you with any issue related to a Collection Point order.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3498db;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/submit-new-request\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #3498db;\">Open a support ticket right here</a></span></p>"
}